Installation 
============

The library CalculusPy may be installed using pip...
  
.. code:: python

    !pip install CalculusPy

The library CalculusPy may be installed using pip...
To import  you can use:

.. code:: python

    from CalculusPy.RiemannSums import plot_riemann_sum
    from CalculusPy.SlopeFields import slope_fields

